title: AMAZING URUGUAY 2013
description:
You always expect a country president to look at least 


dignified and like a statesman, same with ambassadors, 


but some decided to break the rules and install as such 


people you would find in the streets doing one thing or 


another...




I am sure many feel deeply embarrassed by this and the 


State Department should even more, regardless of any 


opportunistic attempt at blending in with the local 


powers that be.  




Please seed, I can only seed for a short time. Thanks.
